msgctxt "0000"
msgid "Sandstorm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0001"
msgid "Gotta go."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm watching the sandstorm.\n"
"Want to join me?<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sandstorms are pretty common out in the\n"
"desert. If you get caught in one, you'll\n"
"get lost for sure..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (long)
#. 5: sound
msgctxt "Talk_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I...want to get to <2.se_co>Gerudo Town<3.re_co>. But they\n"
"told me it'd be too difficult to get there\n"
"right now.<4.pa>\n"
"<5.so>So...I'm just kind of stuck here..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I watch that sandstorm around the clock!\n"
"Every minute of the day! Except when\n"
"I'm sleeping, of course."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>They said it dies down occasionally,\n"
"but I've never seen it happen.<2.pa>\n"
"Did they lie to me?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Urgh, what's the deal with this cold...\n"
"How does it get this cold in the desert?\n"
"I hate the nighttime here."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "Talk_07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I made it all the way to Gerudo Town!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>But I'm not sure why they let me in..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk_08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm?<2.pa> Wait a minute...<3.pa> Didn't I meet you\n"
"at the Kara Kara Bazaar?<4.pa> Or was it\n"
"someone else?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I heard the sandstorm sometimes dies\n"
"down, but it's been going strong the\n"
"entire time I've been watching it.\n"
"I'm going to sleep..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But I hear that sandstorm over there will\n"
"die down for a few hours each day,\n"
"clearing a path.\n"
"I want to visit that huge tower, but the\n"
"sandstorm is in the way, so...I'll just sit\n"
"here and wait for it to die down."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk_11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I heard the sandstorm dies down from\n"
"time to time, and I really want to figure\n"
"out why...<2.pa>and when!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk_50"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The sandstorm is gone, but I'm sure it\n"
"will come back today. <2.pa>Yup, it definitely\n"
"will."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_51"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I was filling my days with watching that\n"
"sandstorm... <2.pa>That's all I did, unless I was\n"
"sleeping."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk_52"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It was always there...<2.pa> So reliable.<3.pa>\n"
"But now it's never there.<4.pa>\n"
"What happened?<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk_53"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I was thinking of going to the giant\n"
"tower, you know.<2.pa> With the sandstorm\n"
"gone, maybe I can go now?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk_54"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm waiting for the sandstorm to appear...<2.pa>\n"
"Wanna sit and wait together?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk_55"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'd heard that the sandstorm\n"
"dies down sometimes, but...<2.pa>\n"
"it seems like it's dead forever.\n"
"I guess I need to find a new hobby.<3.pa>\n"
"Maybe I'll take up sleeping.\n"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_56"
msgid "<1.so>Good morning!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "near00"
msgid "Does it...not go away?"
msgstr ""

